  "title": "Savory Dense Polish Spring Onion Pilaf",
  "description": "A winey, dense, and indulgent Polish dish featuring spring onions, this pilaf is perfect for special occasions. It is made with fry-grind-rice-khao-khua and is satvik-friendly.",
