  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped spring onions and cook until they are softened.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the rice and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the white wine and cook until the liquid is absorbed.",
    "Add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cover the pan with a lid.",
    "Steam the pilaf in a bamboo steamer for 20 minutes.",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and season with salt, black pepper, and dried thyme.",
    "Serve hot."
